image_analysis.description: A photograph showing two fire extinguishers mounted on a white wall in a stairwell. The extinguisher on the left is a standard red dry chemical type. The extinguisher on the right is a larger red CO2 extinguisher with a black discharge horn. Above the extinguishers is a black label with white text. To the left, a wooden banister and its shadow are visible. In the bottom left corner, several bags of 'PROFESSIONAL POTTING MIX' are stacked on the stairs. An electrical outlet is visible on the wall below the extinguishers.
